**Bounded history truncates long scenarios.** `WorldHistoryRecorder` defaults to capacity 64 ticks. Scenarios longer than that with default config silently truncate, producing a non-replayable bundle. Document this prominently in `docs/guides/scenario-runner.md` per A14.

